'''John Dicks''' (born [[July 23]], [[1940s#1947|1947]]) is an actor who played the [[Galactic Empire|Imperial]] officer [[Lennox|Captian Lennox]] in [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''Star Wars'': Episode V ''The Empire Strikes Back'']], commanding the [[Star Destroyer]] ''[[Tyrant]]''. The movie credits him only as "Imperial Officer," but the [[Star Wars Legends|Expanded Universe]] later named him [[Captain]] Lennox.

